npc.name: 冒険者ギルドの調査員

lines: Curses! We can't leave this devilry uninvestigated, but if I leave my post, no one will be keeping an eye on the Impresario. If only an obviously skilled adventurer would pass by...
In order to undertake the quest “The Sinister Soirée,” you must first complete the quest “It's Probably Pirates.”
Have you gained access to the masquerade yet? I hear tell that the Continental Circus has quite outdone itself with the decor this year. No doubt in order to lure in more innocent victims!
Never fear, I will continue to monitor the Impresario's activities without rest! You are free to keep an eye on the happenings within the manor.
